Difference between EBS and EFS and normal storage?
The full form of Amazon EBS is Amazon Elastic Block Store / The full form of Amazon EFS is Amazon Elastic File System
It is used to provide the block-level storage volumes for the use of EC2 instances. /It is simple to use.
It is mainly used for data that should be quickly accessible and requires long term durability. /It is used in modernize application development
It is suitable for both types of database-style applications -:

1. Those rely on random reads

2. Those rely on random writes. /Industries use this for enhancing content management systems
